---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="CalWORKs - Bonita House">
	<!-- Hero Section -->
	<div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-bonita-50 to-bonita-emerald-50 py-16 sm:py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
			<h1 class="text-4xl font-bold tracking-tight text-bonita-slate-900 sm:text-6xl lg:text-7xl">
				CalWORKs Services
			</h1>
			<p class="mt-8 text-xl leading-relaxed text-bonita-slate-700 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Comprehensive support services for CalWORKs participants, helping families achieve self-sufficiency through education, employment, and wraparound support services.
			</p>
		</div>
	</div>
		
	<!-- Mission Section -->
	<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-bonita-600 sm:text-4xl mb-8">
					Supporting CalWORKs Families
				</h2>
			</div>
			<div class="bg-bonita-50 rounded-xl p-8 lg:p-12 border border-bonita-100 shadow-lg">
				<p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-bonita-slate-700 text-center font-medium">
					Our CalWORKs services provide specialized support to help families overcome barriers to employment and education. We understand the unique challenges faced by CalWORKs participants and offer tailored services to address mental health, substance use, domestic violence, and other barriers that may prevent economic self-sufficiency.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Core Services Section -->
	<section class="bg-bonita-slate-50 py-16 sm:py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-bonita-emerald-600 sm:text-4xl mb-8">
					Core Services
				</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8">
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-bonita-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="text-3xl mr-4">📋</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-bonita-slate-800">Comprehensive Assessment</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Thorough evaluation of barriers to employment and development of individualized service plans.</p>
					<ul class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Barrier identification and assessment</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Individual service planning</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Goal setting and milestone tracking</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Regular progress reviews</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
				
				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-bonita-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="text-3xl mr-4">🧠</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-bonita-slate-800">Mental Health Services</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Individual and group counseling to address mental health barriers to employment and education.</p>
					<ul class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Individual therapy and counseling</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Group therapy and support groups</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Crisis intervention services</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Medication management support</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-bonita-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="text-3xl mr-4">🚫</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-bonita-emerald-600">Substance Use Treatment</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Evidence-based treatment for substance use disorders that may interfere with work or education goals.</p>
					<ul class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Individual and group counseling</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Intensive outpatient programs</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Relapse prevention planning</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Family therapy and education</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-bonita-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="text-3xl mr-4">🛡️</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-bonita-600">Domestic Violence Support</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Specialized services for survivors of domestic violence, including safety planning and trauma treatment.</p>
					<ul class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Safety planning and risk assessment</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Trauma-informed counseling</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Support groups for survivors</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Legal advocacy and referrals</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-bonita-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="text-3xl mr-4">💼</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-bonita-emerald-600">Employment Services</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Job readiness training, placement assistance, and ongoing support to maintain employment.</p>
					<ul class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Job readiness and skills training</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Resume writing and interview preparation</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Job placement and search assistance</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-emerald-600 mr-2">✓</span> Workplace support and retention services</li>
					</ul>
				</div>

				<div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-bonita-slate-200 hover:shadow-xl transition-all duration-300 hover:-translate-y-1">
					<div class="flex items-center mb-4">
						<div class="text-3xl mr-4">🎓</div>
						<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-bonita-600">Educational Support</h3>
					</div>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 leading-relaxed mb-4">Support for participants pursuing education and vocational training programs.</p>
					<ul class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm space-y-2">
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Educational planning and guidance</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Academic support and tutoring</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Financial aid assistance</li>
						<li class="flex items-start"><span class="text-bonita-600 mr-2">✓</span> Childcare coordination</li>
					</ul>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<!-- Wraparound Support Services Section -->
	<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-bonita-600 sm:text-4xl mb-8">
					Wraparound Support Services
				</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-8">
				<div class="bg-bonita-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-100">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-bonita-600 mb-6 text-center">Family Support</h3>
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div class="flex gap-4 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-bonita-600">
							<span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">👨‍👩‍👧‍👦</span>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-semibold text-bonita-slate-800 mb-2">Parenting Support</h4>
								<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Classes and support groups focused on positive parenting skills and child development.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-bonita-600">
							<span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">🏠</span>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-semibold text-bonita-slate-800 mb-2">Housing Assistance</h4>
								<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Help finding and maintaining stable housing, including emergency housing resources.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-bonita-600">
							<span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">🚗</span>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-semibold text-bonita-slate-800 mb-2">Transportation Support</h4>
								<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Bus passes, transportation vouchers, and assistance with vehicle repairs.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
				
				<div class="bg-bonita-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-emerald-100">
					<h3 class="text-xl font-semibold text-bonita-emerald-600 mb-6 text-center">Health & Wellness</h3>
					<div class="space-y-4">
						<div class="flex gap-4 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-bonita-emerald-600">
							<span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">⚕️</span>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-semibold text-bonita-slate-800 mb-2">Healthcare Navigation</h4>
								<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Assistance accessing medical care, health insurance enrollment, and care coordination.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-bonita-emerald-600">
							<span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">🧘‍♀️</span>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-semibold text-bonita-slate-800 mb-2">Wellness Programs</h4>
								<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Stress management, mindfulness, and wellness activities to support overall health.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="flex gap-4 bg-white p-4 rounded-lg border-l-4 border-bonita-emerald-600">
							<span class="text-2xl flex-shrink-0">👶</span>
							<div>
								<h4 class="font-semibold text-bonita-slate-800 mb-2">Childcare Support</h4>
								<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Quality childcare referrals and assistance with childcare subsidies and vouchers.</p>
							</div>
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	
	<!-- Program Outcomes Section -->
	<section class="bg-bonita-slate-50 py-16 sm:py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-bonita-emerald-600 sm:text-4xl mb-8">
					Program Outcomes
				</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
				<div class="bg-bonita-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-100 text-center">
					<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-bonita-600 mb-2">85%</div>
					<div class="text-bonita-slate-700 font-medium">Successfully Complete Services</div>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-bonita-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-emerald-100 text-center">
					<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-bonita-emerald-600 mb-2">72%</div>
					<div class="text-bonita-slate-700 font-medium">Gain Employment or Education</div>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-bonita-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-100 text-center">
					<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-bonita-600 mb-2">68%</div>
					<div class="text-bonita-slate-700 font-medium">Achieve Self-Sufficiency</div>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-bonita-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-emerald-100 text-center">
					<div class="text-4xl font-bold text-bonita-emerald-600 mb-2">90%</div>
					<div class="text-bonita-slate-700 font-medium">Report Improved Well-being</div>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
	
	<!-- Getting Started Section -->
	<section class="bg-white py-16 sm:py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-6xl px-6 lg:px-8">
			<div class="mx-auto max-w-2xl text-center mb-16">
				<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-bonita-600 sm:text-4xl mb-8">
					Getting Started
				</h2>
			</div>
			
			<div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-4 gap-6">
				<div class="bg-bonita-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-100 text-center">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-bonita-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">1</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-bonita-600 mb-3">Referral</h3>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Referral from CalWORKs eligibility worker or self-referral for assessment.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-bonita-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-emerald-100 text-center">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-bonita-emerald-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">2</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-bonita-emerald-600 mb-3">Assessment</h3>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Comprehensive assessment to identify barriers and develop service plan.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-bonita-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-100 text-center">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-bonita-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">3</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-bonita-600 mb-3">Services</h3>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Begin individualized services based on assessment and participant goals.</p>
				</div>
				<div class="bg-bonita-emerald-50 rounded-xl p-8 border border-bonita-emerald-100 text-center">
					<div class="w-12 h-12 bg-bonita-emerald-600 text-white rounded-full flex items-center justify-center text-xl font-bold mx-auto mb-4">4</div>
					<h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-bonita-emerald-600 mb-3">Success</h3>
					<p class="text-bonita-slate-600 text-sm">Achieve employment, education, or self-sufficiency goals with ongoing support.</p>
				</div>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>

	<section class="bg-bonita-gradient py-16 sm:py-24">
		<div class="mx-auto max-w-4xl px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-4xl mb-8">
				Ready to Take the Next Step?
			</h2>
			<p class="text-xl leading-relaxed text-bonita-100 mb-12 max-w-2xl mx-auto">
				Our CalWORKs services are designed to help you overcome barriers and achieve your goals for economic self-sufficiency. Contact us today to learn more about how we can support you and your family.
			</p>
			<div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row justify-center gap-4">
				<a href="/contact" 
				   class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full bg-white px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-bonita-600 shadow-lg hover:bg-bonita-50 focus-visible:outline focus-visible:outline-2 focus-visible:outline-offset-2 focus-visible:outline-white transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
					Get Started Today
					<svg class="ml-2 -mr-1 w-5 h-5" fill="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 20 20" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
						<path fill-rule="evenodd" d="M10.293 3.293a1 1 0 011.414 0l6 6a1 1 0 010 1.414l-6 6a1 1 0 01-1.414-1.414L14.586 11H3a1 1 0 110-2h11.586l-4.293-4.293a1 1 0 010-1.414z" clip-rule="evenodd"></path>
					</svg>
				</a>
				<a href="/contact" 
				   class="inline-flex items-center rounded-full border-2 border-white px-8 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white hover:bg-white hover:text-bonita-600 transition-all duration-300 hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1">
					Ask Questions
				</a>
			</div>
		</div>
	</section>
</Layout>